			<h3>TLC Soft Tissue Management</h3>
			<p>
				TLC Soft Tissue Management (STM) is a professional and personal system developed for early detection, diagnosis, treatment, and maintenance of periodontal disease.  Its regular re-evaluations and periodontal maintenance are designed to prevent tooth loss and the need for periodontal surgery.
			</p>
