				<li>Regular use of a TLC tongue cleaner to remove bacterial build-up, food debris, fungi, and dead 		   cells from the surface of the tongue</li>
				<li>Regular use of a 0.12% Chlorhexidine Gluconate rinse during infections</li>
				<li>Regular use of Listerine use for maintenance</li>
